body:
**Hey there hi there ! :)**

I&#039;m back with a new post, this time for MMR and ELO. A friend of mine was explaining what it consisted in but I was on the Rift at the same time and didn&#039;t understand anything at all x) We came to talk about it because (for those who knew me before this post) I finally reached level 30 and started playing ranked.

Ranked games though. Here are some of the first thoughts I had in mind when I played my first Ranked games:

&quot;Woop woop! Gonna try something new, can&#039;t wait!&quot;
&quot;Damn that was long, but finally in the lobby&quot;
&quot;HOLY MOTHER OF CRAP I THINK I BROKE MY LOL CLIENT! I CAN&#039;T SELECT MY CHAMPION!&quot;
&quot;Wait are they actually banning champions? Are they seriously banning Urgot? WHY? I&#039;ve never seen him ingame!&quot;
&quot;Damn it, I don&#039;t even own that many junglers xD&quot;
&quot;Ah... People fighting over position and &quot;call order&quot; &quot;pick order&quot;. Wondering if people actually want to be useful to a team or just get kills. Which is useful. But not always. I guess. Bah&quot;
&quot;Damn the pressure. People are WAY bolder in ranked games. Like, seriously? What was this 5v2 at 7 minutes bottom lane? xD&quot;
&quot;YOUHOUUU I got my first rank ever and it&#039;s not even really representative of me since it won&#039;t count in season 6 :D&quot;

There you go, I ended up Silver I and now I&#039;m in Gold V :)

But I still don&#039;t get what MMR and ELO are, can you guys explain? Where and how do I find it? 

There, enough of that, I gotta practice my {{champion:28}} , I seriously suck at playing her.

PS: See you around :D
PPS: Thank you Riot ^^
PPPS: Be nice to people!

_**Aerie**_
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}

replies.body:
Hah that's nice of you to say that, though I don't think I'm "better", I just have more fun and I don't forget the essential: games are for fun, let's miss some Creeps here and there with {{champion:21}} , just better show dem enemies how a well timed Bullet Time hurts and laugh in synch ^^
See you around buddy :)

{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}
